Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time it takes to complete 'Accepted + In Progress' before reaching 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + In Progress' to be followed by 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + In Progress' before reaching 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in comparison to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time it takes for 'Accepted + In Progress' to transition to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to the next occurrence of 'Accepted + In Progress'
